OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Residents wait
OL,4,Cyears for tax refunds
OL,6,FA Guernsey accountancy firm has told
OL,7,FITV News that almost half the tax
OL,8,Freturns it submitted were returned
OL,9,Fwith incorrect assessments.
OL,11,FThe director of TCS Guernsey, Tim
OL,12,FChilestone, explains: "If we go by
OL,13,Fassessments that we have seen for
OL,14,F2022, which is the most recent year we
OL,15,Fhave generally got assessments for,
OL,16,Fout of all the returns we have
OL,17,Fsubmitted, I'd say revenue services
OL,18,Fmiscalculated around 45% of them."
