OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Residents wait
OL,4,Cyears for tax refunds
OL,6,FSome residents also claim they have
OL,7,Fbeen continually chased for fines they
OL,8,Fdo not understand and are waiting
OL,9,Fyears for refund payments.
OL,11,FSimon French says he has spent years
OL,12,Ftrying to get his late father's tax
OL,13,Frebate of #200, adding: "I was told
OL,14,Fthe case had gone on a priority list
OL,15,Fand the money would be paid again
OL,16,Fwithin a few weeks.
