OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Residents wait
OL,4,Cyears for tax refunds
OL,6,F"I still haven't had any money and
OL,7,Fhave since been told again that they
OL,8,Faren't able to issue rebates or
OL,9,Fassessments, but if they can't issue
OL,10,Fassessments, then surely they must be
OL,11,Fguessing what people owe them.
OL,13,F"It's not really about the money
OL,14,Fbecause I will have to split that
OL,15,Fbetween my sisters, so it's not going
OL,16,Fto go far, but it's the principle of
OL,17,Fit. They owe money to me and my
OL,18,Fsisters.
