OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Residents wait
OL,4,Cyears for tax refunds
OL,6,F"If I owed them money, I'd get a
OL,7,Fletter threatening court action, so
OL,8,Fwhy can't I do the same?"
OL,10,FSimilarly, Danny Cook claims he has
OL,11,Fbeen tackling a tax bill of #1,500.
OL,13,FHe says: "Enough is enough, they need
OL,14,Fto get themselves in order so they
OL,15,Faren't sending people out bills like
OL,16,Fthis when people don't actually owe
OL,17,Fthe bills.
