OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Residents wait
OL,4,Cyears for tax refunds
OL,6,F"Every year, I get my tax and
OL,7,Finsurance deducted from my wages, and
OL,8,Fmost years they end up paying me the
OL,9,Fmoney back.
OL,11,F"They send me a bill and tell me they
OL,12,Fare going to give me money, but on the
OL,13,Fother hand, they then say we want that
OL,14,Fback, telling me, 'You now owe us'.
OL,16,F"It seems to be happening too
OL,17,Ffrequently. I just don't know what to
OL,18,Fdo about it."
