OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Residents wait
OL,4,Cyears for tax refunds
OL,6,FAdding to his frustrations, Danny says
OL,7,Fit has been difficult to get an answer
OL,8,Ffrom Guernsey's Revenue Service when
OL,9,Fhe has tried to contact them.
OL,11,FHe adds: "I have had nothing back from
OL,12,Fthem at all, and I have sent letters.
OL,14,F"We sent the last bill in, a
OL,15,Frecalculation of that tax to 100% to
OL,16,Fmake sure I owe the right amount. We
OL,17,Fworked it out and it came back fine,
OL,18,Fbut then they are still saying we owe
OL,19,Fthem #1,500 and I just don't know
OL,20,Fwhere they are getting them from."
