OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Residents wait
OL,4,Cyears for tax refunds
OL,6,FHowever, the Guernsey Revenue Service
OL,7,Fstresses that assessments are correct
OL,8,Fin most cases and when there is an
OL,9,Ferror, it can be down to taxpayers
OL,10,Fthemselves.
OL,12,FHead of Service Delivery, Scott
OL,13,FBloomfield, explains: "It's a minority
OL,14,Fof people that will receive an
OL,15,Fincorrect bill, that's not always the
OL,16,Ffault of the Revenue Service.
OL,18,F"It may be that the details that were
OL,19,Fsubmitted by the customer were
OL,20,Fincorrect.
