OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Residents wait
OL,4,Cyears for tax refunds
OL,6,F"The backlog is getting much better.
OL,7,FWe have been going through a
OL,8,Ftransformation of our IT systems, and
OL,9,Fthese are very much up and running, so
OL,10,Fwe are able to start issuing more
OL,11,Fassessments.
OL,13,F"We have issued 9,000 tax assessments
OL,14,Fthis year, 20,000 contribution
OL,15,Fassessments and approximately 500
OL,16,Fassessments a day."
